caption.text:
Influence map tagged by @nigetajesson (LONG POST)

From top left - bottom, centre top-botom, top right-bottom
1. Masashi Kishimoto, i love his clean lines and character proportions ‚ô° 
2. @daviddownton is on of my favorite fashion illustrator of all time 
3. Shigenori Soejima, since i jumped into Persona fandom, i instantly fell in love with his persona designs as well as his concept arts. And became a huge influence to my designs
4. Takegarou. i watched Katanagatari and finally found the character designer. His/her cute, colorful designs are really inspiring!
5. Tknk / dahlia-art. Another all time favorite fashion illustrator. Simple yet stunning ‚ô°
6. Chisami Tsuchiya (apricot8585), back in 2008/2009, i met this artist on dA. Personally, she's really lovely and kind. We had some chit chat on messenger and i really adore this person. After she deactiveted her account, i can't find her anywhere else and hoped to get a chance to meet her once again ;;;
7. @paulabonet . Dem smooth strokes ‚ô°
8. Ask@pixiv. Anime style, tones, composition, and everything are just gorgeous on his/her hand ‚ô° 
9. @toolkit04 admirable senpie with his beautiful-melancholic portraits is just too hard to resist. I really love his pencil strokes.
10. @elfandiary yes. More admirable senpie. I adore his watercolor works and markers

Since  there not much space-- 11. Hiroyuki Takei (Shaman King). My first art influence but i don't have enough space to put his works orz".
12. Loish (@loisvb) dem paintings and colors ‚ô°

caption.text:
I won't stop developing my original characters. No matter how many times i redesigned them. Kirana Kusnapaharani is always been one of my favorite. 
Sebenarnya gw punya sedikit cerita tentang Kirana ini. Desainnya sederhana dan merakyat sekali. Tapi beberapa lama kemudian, variasi bajunya makin banyak dan modis. Kebanyakan menggunakan kebaya modern dan pakaian daerah. Dulu bahkan sempet berlama2 di toko buku cuman buat liat desain kebaya modern dari macem2 desainer lokal spt Anne Avantie juga.

Setelah beberapa tahun, gw hiatus gambar Kirana karena sempet muak dan give up. Tapi akhirnya toh gw kangen juga sama cewek ini. Setelah digambar2 lagi, Kirana ternyata masih bisa dikembangin lagi dikembangin lagi.. terus2an. Gimanapun gue gambar, gak bosen aja. And thats how you develop a character. caption.text:
No matter what society and fashion industry says, every body shapes are beautiful. Even when people calls you 'whale', be happy. Whale is a sweet animal, they sing beutifully, friendly with others. It is better to be a healthy whale than an anorexic, skinny bones. 
Although, beauty comes from inside when you finally accepts who you really are, and be happy with it. 
You are beautiful in your own way. Live it. ---- IMO, fat is girl's number 1 problem when it comes to beauty. But in fact we're just too much staring at models, we want to be like them, a tall fair body. 
I don't like it when people or society commenting on a certain person and call them 'fat' or 'whale'. You don't realize that you have broke the girl's heart, that they hold them dearly and you suddenly broke 'em. 
A simple illustration, yes. But i hope what i said above would encourage some person who's not confident enough about their body size. 
Another series themed 'beauty' will coming soon. ; )
